277
00:14:42,160 --> 00:14:44,060
to fix the knife in place, would you?

278
00:14:44,060 --> 00:14:46,960
It'll fall easier too if the top is heavy.

279
00:14:46,960 --> 00:14:48,360
I see!

280
00:14:48,360 --> 00:14:51,160
If so, after the knife stabs the victim,

281
00:14:51,160 --> 00:14:52,360
the books would slide down,

282
00:14:52,360 --> 00:14:54,060
and the victim would fall to the floor

283
00:14:54,060 --> 00:14:55,760
