284
00:14:55,760 --> 00:14:57,460
All he has to do after that is put the bookshelf back

285
00:14:57,460 --> 00:14:59,260
and pick up the books that are scattered,

286
00:14:59,260 --> 00:15:01,760
so no one realizes that anything had been rigged.

287
00:15:01,760 --> 00:15:04,360
But, sonny,

288
00:15:04,360 --> 00:15:06,760
if there were to be a knife sticking out of the bookshelf,

289
00:15:06,760 --> 00:15:09,760
my wife would have noticed it.

290
00:15:09,760 --> 00:15:11,260
All right, then.

291
00:15:12,560 --> 00:15:14,860
There! What if it's placed like this?

292
00:15:14,860 --> 00:15:15,960
What the...

293
00:15:15,960 --> 00:15:17,360
I see!

294
00:15:17,360 --> 00:15:19,460
That way the knife would be hidden

295
00:15:19,460 --> 00:15:23,160
and it explains why the knife had stabbed the victim from the side.

296
00:15:23,160 --> 00:15:25,060
You're really something, sonny.

297
00:15:25,060 --> 00:15:27,260
Besides, even if the officers were to get here before the killer

298
00:15:27,260 --> 00:15:30,060
