299
00:15:30,060 --> 00:15:32,960
it would just look like the victim had struggled with the killer

300
00:15:32,960 --> 00:15:36,260
and it wouldn't even dawn on anyone

301
00:15:36,260 --> 00:15:39,460
that there had ever been something rigged here.

302
00:15:39,460 --> 00:15:43,060
Well, how about it, Mr. Masuo?

