00:19:15,960 --> 00:19:17,660
Two hours later,

368
00:19:17,660 --> 00:19:20,360
the two robbers who were at their condo counting cash

369
00:19:20,360 --> 00:19:22,960
were arrested.

370
00:19:22,960 --> 00:19:25,660
Thus, two cases were solved at once.

371
00:19:29,660 --> 00:19:31,960
According to Mr. Masuo's testimony,

