00:21:21,260 --> 00:21:23,360
Just as expected of you!

378
00:21:23,360 --> 00:21:26,260
It was no big deal, Superintendent Matsumoto.

379
00:21:26,260 --> 00:21:30,460
Such simple case hardly require my attention.

380
00:21:30,460 --> 00:21:33,160
That's right. Because the case was solved...

